{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>據了解，涉事航班為CX216，由英國曼徹斯特城返港。死者51歲，持本港身份證。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260424/1124251729680928768190358.jpeg/EB4d0Z97rl7ziZ3_RczFhiw98V4G5HiA_jyKeP48ing\" alt=\"51歲男子在航機上昏迷，其後證實不治。（資料圖片）\"><figcaption>51歲男子在航機上昏迷，其後證實不治。（資料圖片）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-24T00:06:51.079226+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":65,"images":1,"source":"HK01 突發","fallback":"none"}}